    <stitle>International&#174; MaxxForce&#8482; DT, 9 and 10 Engine Service Manual - Diamond Logic&#174; Engine Brake -
        Installation - Brake Shut-off Valve (BSV) Assembly
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>Brake Shut-off Valve (BSV) Assembly</title>
        <figure id="f3350008237" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figK08/K08006.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Brake Shut-off Valve seals</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">O-ring</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Back-up ring (2)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">O-ring</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para id="s0814" count="1">Install new O-rings and back-up rings on brake shut-off valve.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lubricate O-rings with clean engine oil.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f3350008213" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figK11/K11019.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Brake shut-off valve</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install brake shut-off valve in high-pressure oil manifold.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten brake shut-off valve to special torque.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f3350008212" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figK11/K11018.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>BSV assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Solenoid</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Solenoid nut</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Harness connector</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install solenoid over the brake shut-off valve.</para>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <caution>
                <para>To prevent engine damage, position BSV solenoid harness connector to give proper clearance for
                    rocker arm movement.
                </para>
            </caution>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install solenoid nut and position BSV solenoid harness connector to give proper clearance
                for rocker arm movement.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten solenoid nut to special torque.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect UVC harness connector to BSV assembly</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
